import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['delay'] = pd.to_numeric(data['delay'], errors='coerce')
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='delay', kde=True, color='blue')
    plt.axvline(data['delay'].median(), color='red', label=f'Median: {data["delay"].median():.2f}')
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of delay time?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['distance'] = pd.to_numeric(data['distance'], errors='coerce')
    avg_distance = data['distance'].mean()
    ax = sns.barplot(x='distance', y='distance', data=data, estimator=lambda x: len(x) / len(data) * 100, color='blue')
    ax.axvline(avg_distance, color='red', label=f'Average distance: {avg_distance:.2f}')
    ax.set(xlabel='Distance', ylabel='Percentage of flights')
    ax.legend()
    return plt

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='coerce')
    data = data.dropna(subset=['date'])
    data['year'] = data['date'].dt.year
    data['month'] = data['date'].dt.month
    data['year_month'] = data['date'].dt.strftime('%Y-%m')
    data = data.groupby(['origin', 'destination']).size().reset_index(name='counts')
    data = data.pivot(index='origin', columns='destination', values='counts')
    sns.heatmap(data, cmap='Blues', annot=True, fmt='d', linewidths=.5)
    plt.title('Which origin and destination pairs are the most common?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='coerce')
    chart = sns.boxplot(x='origin', y='delay', data=data)
    chart.axhline(data['delay'].median(), color='red', label='Median: {:.2f}'.format(data['delay'].median()))
    chart.set(title='What is the distribution of delay time by origin?')
    chart.legend()
    return chart

chart = plot(data)
